FOR THOSE

SIGNIFICANT PENDING LEGAL PROCEEDINGS THAT DO NOT APPEAR IN THE TABLE AND THAT

ARE NOT THE SUBJECT OF PENDING SETTLEMENT AGREEMENTS, THE COMPANY HAS

DETERMINED THAT LIABILITY IS NOT PROBABLE OR THE AMOUNT OF THE LIABILITY IS NOT

ESTIMABLE, OR BOTH, AND THE COMPANY IS UNABLE TO ESTIMATE THE POSSIBLE LOSS OR

RANGE OF LOSS AT THIS TIME. THE

107

