SHARES UNDER OPTION INCLUDE GRANTS FROM PREVIOUS PLANS. FOR OPTIONS OUTSTANDING

AT DECEMBER 31, 2009, THE WEIGHTED-AVERAGE REMAINING CONTRACTUAL LIFE WAS

