ITEM 10.

DIRECTORS, EXECUTIVE OFFICERS AND CORPORATE GOVERNANCE.

THE INFORMATION RELATING TO DIRECTORS AND

NOMINEES OF 3M IS SET FORTH UNDER THE CAPTION PROPOSAL NO. 1  ELECTION

OF DIRECTORS IN 3MS PROXY STATEMENT FOR ITS ANNUAL MEETING OF STOCKHOLDERS TO

